               <p>Before Mr. Justice Gaselee.</p>
               <p>1538. 
               
                  <persName id="t18341016-63-defend686" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     JOYCE
                  <interp inst="t18341016-63-defend686" type="surname" value="JOYCE"></interp>
