                     <interp inst="t18341016-63-person693" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , tailor, No. 26, Colonade, Russell-square, and 
               <persName id="t18341016-63-person694">
                  Joseph 
                  Lee
               <interp inst="t18341016-63-person694" type="surname" value="Lee"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18341016-63-person694" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18341016-63-person694" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , butcher, Osseden-street, gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
